Career Break: Transition to Data Science & Machine Learning
- Dedicated time to pivot from nursing into data science and ML
- Studied Python, SQL, statistical modeling, and machine learning fundamentals
- Combined clinical background with technical skills to prepare for healthcare data roles



Student Nurse, Ashton Living Center, Ashton, ID
- Assisted registered nurses in patient care and discharge planning
- Gained experience in medication administration, wound care, and EMR documentation
- Ensured HIPAA compliance and contributed to patient education



English Teacher, CARROT Global (Remote)
- Taught conversational and business English to professionals abroad
- Adapted lessons to student proficiency levels and learning goals



ACT Math Tutor, Private Family Hire, Draper, UT
- Designed custom lesson plans and tracked ACT math performance
- Used assessment tools to guide students toward milestone achievements



Report Manager Intern, Redstone Residential
- Conducted real estate data analysis for investment strategies
- Led DEI projects and streamlined internal documentation
- Coordinated corporate events and employee surveys
